{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/Header_AboutTheGame.png?t=1739304788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow your small gem business in this short casual simulation miner, Gemporium! Manage your time wisely between <strong>mining up gemstones</strong>, <strong>refining them for more profit</strong> and <strong>selling them to awaiting customers</strong>. After you inherit a small shop and prospecting license  from your grandmother, you quickly realize it also came with a price of <strong>generational debt.</strong> Now on top of building your business you must appease the <strong>Loan Shark</strong> and break even before you go broke!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gemporium features a day cycle similar to Stardew Valley, where there is only so much time in the day for you to complete tasks and run the gem store. Each day consists of:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/Header_Mining.png?t=1739304788\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong> deeper and deeper in the local mines to stock up on all sorts of Gems. Utilize different mining tools in order to prevent cracks and maintain the highest quality product for your shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/GemporiumExcavationDEMO.gif?t=1739304788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/Header_Refining.png?t=1739304788\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Polish</strong> and prepare your recent finds in the mine to convert those lumps of rock into something collectors adore! Unrefined gemstones sell for way less than their refined counterparts, so make sure to visit the refinement table before you set up shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/GemporiumRefinementAmethyst.gif?t=1739304788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/Header_Selling.png?t=1739304788\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sell</strong> your stockpile of gems to eagerly awaiting customers, but make sure to keep their tastes in mind to maximize your profit and increase your shop's reputation! The shop is only open for a certain amount of time a day so don't be late!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/extras/GemporiumShop.gif?t=1739304788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739304788","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/page.bg.jpg?t=1739304788","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/63e94710b42ba4733ec8dbd5258c73a2e958331f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739304788","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836100/63e94710b42ba4733ec8dbd5258c73a2e958331f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739304788","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3466550,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p